    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "――という感じで、雫ちゃんに誘ってもらった\nアイドルのライブが最高だったの",
      "startTime": 3.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いい刺激になったんですね、良かったです",
      "startTime": 6.9823582966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう！　私ももっともーっと頑張ろうって思えたの\n佐伯遙子、また明日からがんがん行くわよ！",
      "startTime": 16.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いけない。そろそろスーパーに行かないと",
      "startTime": 20.3451750755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "買い出しなら手伝いましょうか？\n俺も今日の仕事はもう終わりなので",
      "startTime": 26.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　そんな、悪いわよ……と言いたいけど\nせっかくなら厚意に甘えちゃおうかな",
      "startTime": 35.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうね、付き合ってもらって",
      "startTime": 38.6833836238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どういたしまして。……それにしても\n最近よく遙子さんが買い出しに行ってませんか？",
      "startTime": 44.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "今のサニピってもの凄く忙しいでしょ？\nそれに私以外は高校生で、沢山予定が詰まってるし",
      "startTime": 51.9212495343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "だからみんなの負担を少しでも減らそうと思って\n料理当番を積極的に買って出てるってわけ",
      "startTime": 61.2447529475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "その心遣いはとてもありがたいですけど\n遙子さんだって大学が忙しいんじゃないですか？",
      "startTime": 68.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "私はほら、アイドルのお仕事があんまりない時に\n単位を取りまくっちゃったから",
      "startTime": 76.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "なんていうか、結構融通が利くのよ\nあくまで多少ね？　多少だから！",
      "startTime": 83.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あー……なんというかその、すみません",
      "startTime": 86.9760926882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、もう。そんな真剣に謝らなくっていいってば\nそれじゃあ、そろそろ行こっか",
      "startTime": 97.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、お惣菜コーナーから試食のいい匂いが……\n衝動買いしないように気を付けないと",
      "startTime": 108.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 102
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとくらい買ってもいいんじゃないですか？",
      "startTime": 112.2465587298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "ダメよ！　ちょっと油断して食べる物を\n増やそうものなら……大変なことになるんだから！",
      "startTime": 117.7999913533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "この間だって、お仕事の差し入れでもらったケーキを\n食べてたら、怜ちゃんに凄い顔されたの",
      "startTime": 124.9999913533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "「衣装が入らなくなっちゃいますよ？」……なんて\n爆弾を落とされたんだから！",
      "startTime": 132.2801659449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だもん、気を付けてるから……むちっとしてても\n体重は増えてないし……むちっとはしてるけど……",
      "startTime": 140.3263275057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは失礼しました……\nまさかそこまでシビアだとは",
      "startTime": 148.76665802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "そういう訳だから、女の子に軽率に\n誘惑を持ち掛けないように！",
      "startTime": 154.4333246867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "ハッ！　お菓子の特売……！？\nだ、ダメよ、負けちゃダメ、遙子……！",
      "startTime": 162.4999913533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（ほ、本当に大変なんだな……）",
      "startTime": 166.916403834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "えーっと、野菜はこれくらいでいいかな\n次はお肉ね。今日は確か鶏肉が安くなってたから……",
      "startTime": 176.5333246867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "凄い手際だな……ん？\nはい、もしもし",
      "startTime": 186.7333246867,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2249.0859188999934,
          "startTime": 184.1999913533
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4382.4192522000085,
          "startTime": 186.3333246866
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ではいったんこちらで検討させていただきます\nなるべく今日か明日にはお返事をしますので。それでは",
      "startTime": 192.4333246867,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7979.086033399994,
          "startTime": 196.41665802
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事の依頼？",
      "startTime": 196.9350508214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "今度海沿いの街にオープンするリゾート施設の\n広報大使を遙子さんに務めてほしいそうです",
      "startTime": 201.6615667423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
